metadata.name: Hyperbolic
metadata.description:
Raga Saga Ep:1 (RARE x MENJI)

Raga Saga is a 4 piece series telling the story of boy named Rare and his journey into an upcoming battle. Inspired by some of favorite anime scenes and artists, 

 Ep1: features Artists @M33NJI iconic style

Hyperbolic is my FND "Genesis Drop" after nearly a year of hard battles traversing the peak and valleys of the foreign realm he found himself transported to a young man by the name of Rare has retreated to his healing chamber in preparation for what he believes to be the greatest battle of his life!

Inspired by DBZ & a JuiceWRLD cover created by @yalocalgod LLJ 999 4EVA

5000 x 5000 px
300 DPI

15% of the proceeds to be split with menji in honor of his style.
